  "A student wants to test whether sugar dissolves faster in hot water than in cold water. What is the independent variable in this experiment?": "",
  "The time it takes for the sugar to dissolve completely": "",
  "The temperature of the water used in each trial of the test": "",
  "The amount of sugar added to each cup of water being tested": "",
  "The type of cup used to hold the water during the experiment": "",
  "The independent variable is the water temperature because it is the factor the student deliberately changes. The dependent variable would be the dissolving time.": "",
  "A student tests how light affects plant growth. She places one plant in sunlight and one in a dark closet but uses different soil for each plant. What mistake did she make?": "",
