  "She changed two variables instead of keeping soil the same": "",
  "She forgot to include a hypothesis before starting the test": "",
  "She should have placed both plants in the dark closet first": "",
  "By using different soil, the student changed two variables (light and soil type) at once. For a fair test, only the independent variable (light) should change while everything else stays constant.": "",
